column2: SELECT top #  g.h_beta_flux,   g.h_alpha_flux, g.oiii_#_flux, g.nii_#_flux,  g.oi_#_flux, g.oii_#_flux, g.oii_#_flux, g.neiii_#_flux, s.z, l.fiberMag_u, l.fiberMag_g, l.fiberMag_r,  l.fiberMag_i, l.fiberMag_z, l.fiberMagErr_u,  l.fiberMagErr_g,  l.fiberMagErr_r,  l.fiberMagErr_i, l.fiberMagErr_z, l.extinction_u, l.extinction_g, l.extinction_r, l.extinction_i, l.extinction_z  FROM PhotoObj AS g  JOIN SpecObj AS m  ON m.specobjid = g.specobjid  JOIN SpecObj AS s  ON s.specobjid = g.specobjid   JOIN SpecObj AS i  ON s.specobjid = i.specobjid   JOIN PhotoObjAll as l  ON s.specobjid = l.specobjid  JOIN SpecObj AS e  ON s.specobjid = e.specobjid  WHERE  h_alpha_flux>#  AND h_beta_flux>#  AND oi_#_flux>#  AND oiii_#_flux>#   AND nii_#_flux>#  AND neiii_#_flux>#  AND s.z<#  AND s.z>#  AND s.zwarning=#  AND i.sn_median>#  AND sigma_balmer<#  AND oii_#_flux>#  AND oii_#_flux>#  AND e.AoN_NeIII_#>#  AND e.AoN_OII_#>#  AND e.AoN_OII_#># AND (fiberMag_u-fiberMag_r) > # AND (fiberMag_u-fiberMag_r) < # AND (fiberMag_u > # AND fiberMag_u < #) AND (fiberMag_g > # AND fiberMag_g < #) AND (fiberMag_r > # AND fiberMag_r < #) AND (fiberMag_i > # AND fiberMag_i < #) AND (fiberMag_z > # AND fiberMag_z < #)
